&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This &lt;strong&gt;Principal Researcher&lt;/strong&gt; will contribute to large-scale &lt;strong&gt;implementation&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;initiatives for federal health agencies. The ideal candidate will bring deep experience in monitoring frameworks, analytic design, alternative payment models, and federal program operations—particularly Centers for Medicare &amp;amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) and the CMS Innovation Center (CMMI).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
